      hed={"Technical Consultation"}
      dek="I provide technical consultation services to help clients choose the right technology stack for their projects, and provide recommendations for best practices and architecture."
      icon={`<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 32 32"><path class="fill-gray-600" d="M11 24h10v2H11zm2 4h6v2h-6zm3-26A10 10 0 0 0 6 12a9.19 9.19 0 0 0 3.46 7.62c1 .93 1.54 1.46 1.54 2.38h2c0-1.84-1.11-2.87-2.19-3.86A7.2 7.2 0 0 1 8 12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0a7.2 7.2 0 0 1-2.82 6.14c-1.07 1-2.18 2-2.18 3.86h2c0-.92.53-1.45 1.54-2.39A9.18 9.18 0 0 0 26 12A10 10 0 0 0 16 2z"/></svg>`}
